zm_toxic_house2_v4
==================

This map is a remake from CS 1.6. I did it as realisticly as i could, I also added some secrets and a basement. Anybody who has played counter-strike 1.6 on a zombie server will undoubtebly remember this map to it's very detail. i've spent a lot of my time on it to make it good and playable. So now i'm sharing this map with you guys, enjoy!
